These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, woodworking
The people have 2 different jobs:  journalist, fisherman
1. the journalist is in an even position##4
2. the fisherman is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | woodworking | writing |
| Job     | fisherman    | journalist   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, water
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is handball is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | water | tea        |
| Sport      | handball  | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, reggae
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, french
1. the italian is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae    | classical |
| Nationality   | italian | french |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate
There 2 different types of food: plum, cabbage
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person eating cabbage is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | tea      | hot-chocolate |
| Food       | plum | cabbage    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
