 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, ice-hockey
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, bus
1. the person driving the quad-bike is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | ice-hockey | sailing  |
| Transport   | bus  | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
